            About Me
          
          
            
              I am originally from Buffalo, NY and now living in Santa Barbara, CA. I’m pursuing a master’s degree from UCSB in environmental science and management. I love talking about going for walks on the beach, trying new restaurants, and dreaming of places to go once we can travel again.
